ngs in the ordinary course of their respective businesses.  For", "bbox": [96.1, 847.6, 1141.6, 868.1]}, {"text": "information regarding legal proceedings that could have a material effect on NEE or FPL, see Note 14 - Legal Proceedings.  Such", "bbox": [96.1, 869.6, 1141.7, 890.1]}, {"text": "descriptions are incorporated herein by reference.", "bbox": [96.1, 891.7, 501.6, 912.2]}, {"text": "Item 4.  Mine Safety Disclosures", "bbox": [96.1, 958.4, 407.2, 981.2]}, {"text": "Not applicable", "bbox": [96.1, 1004.4, 212.6, 1024.9]}, {"text": "PART II", "bbox": [583.4, 1070.8, 655.3, 1093.6]}, {"text": "Item 5.  Market for Registrants' Common Equity, Related Stockholder Matters and Issuer Purchases of Equity", "bbox": [96.1, 1117.7, 1147.7, 1140.5]}, {"text": "Securities", "bbox": [96.1, 1142.3, 193.8, 1165.0]}, {"text": "Common Stock Data.  All of FPL's common stock is owned by NEE.  NEE's common stock is traded on the New York Stock", "bbox": [96.1, 1188.8, 1146.9, 1211.6]}, {"text": "Exchange under the symbol \"NEE.\"  The high and low sales prices for the common stock of NEE as reported in the consolidated", "bbox": [96.1, 1212.7, 1146.7, 1233.2]}, {"text": "transaction reporting system of the New York Stock Exchange and the cash dividends per share declared for each quarter during", "bbox": [96.1, 1234.8, 1146.9, 1255.3]}, {"text": "the past two years are as follows:", "bbox": [96.1, 1256.8, 367.8, 1277.4]}, {"text": "Quarter", "bbox": [226.2, 1361.6, 288.5, 1382.1]}, {"text": "First", "bbox": [102.3, 1390.2, 138.0, 1410.7]}, {"text": "Second", "bbox": [102.3, 1418.8, 164.6, 1439.3]}, {"text": "Third", "bbox": [102.3, 1447.4, 144.1, 1467.9]}, {"text": "Fourth", "bbox": [102.3, 1476.0, 155.4, 1496.5]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [583.9, 1314.6, 624.7, 1335.2]}, {"text": "High", "bbox": [464.2, 1361.6, 502.0, 1382.1]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [433.1, 1390.2, 443.4, 1410.7]}, {"text": "55.86", "bbox": [487.2, 1390.2, 533.1, 1410.7]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [433.1, 1418.8, 4